Standards-Version: 4.6.2

Package: secubox-voip
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), python3-uvicorn
Recommends: docker.io | podman
Description: VoIP/PBX management module for SecuBox
 SecuBox module for managing Asterisk/FreePBX PBX system via Docker.
 Provides extension management, trunk configuration, call routing,
 IVR menus, voicemail, and call detail records.
 .
 Features:
  - Docker/Podman container management
  - Extension and voicemail management
  - SIP trunk configuration
  - Inbound/outbound route management
  - IVR menu builder
  - Call detail records (CDR)
  - SIP peer status monitoring
 .
 Ported from OpenWRT luci-app-voip pattern.
 Provides FastAPI backend on /api/v1/voip/ via Unix socket.
